description: Lists all attribute groups which you have access to. Results are paginated.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The globally unique attribute group identifier of the attribute group.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon resource name (ARN) that specifies the attribute group across services.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the attribute group.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the attribute group that the user provides.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The ISO-8601 formatted timestamp of the moment the attribute group was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The ISO-8601 formatted timestamp of the moment the attribute group was last updated. This time is the same as the creationTime for a newly created attribute group.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The service principal that created the attribute group.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to get the next page of results after a previous API call.
